<mvc:View xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" controllerName="com.cu.s4hana.zlpuba002_1.controller.PoNewItem" xmlns:uxap="sap.uxap" xmlns="sap.m"
	xmlns:layout="sap.ui.layout" xmlns:form="sap.ui.layout.form" xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" >
	<Page
		id="idPoNewItemPage"
		title="{i18n>Label.PoListTitle}"
		showHeader="true" 
		showNavButton="true">
		<customHeader>
			<Bar>
				<contentLeft>
					<Button type="Back" press="handleBackPress" />
				</contentLeft>
				<contentMiddle>
					<Title text="{i18n>Label.PoListTitle}"/>
				</contentMiddle>
				<contentRight>
					<Button id="idGoToPreviousItem" icon="sap-icon://media-reverse" iconFirst="true" type="Default" press="handleGoToPreviousItem"/>
					<Select id="idSelectItem"
						forceSelection="false"
						change="handleItemChange"
						items="{
							path: 'poItem>/',
							sorter: { path: 'EBELP' }
						}">
						<core:Item key="{poItem>EBELP}" text="[{path:'poItem>EBELP', formatter:'.formatter.parseInt'}] {poItem>TXZ01}" />
					</Select>
					<Button id="idGoToNextItem" icon="sap-icon://media-play" iconFirst="false" type="Default" press="handleGoToNextItem"/>
				</contentRight>
			</Bar>
		</customHeader>
		<footer/>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>